00:01:12.162 --> 00:01:17.717
Now of course, once Europe becomes 
one, they’ll know what they are.

00:01:18.002 --> 00:01:24.515
They don’t have any talents, as the 
other people have, none of the talents.

00:01:24.885 --> 00:01:30.645
Just in their pride and arrogance, they 
remained in some sort of a fools’ paradise.

00:01:31.845 --> 00:01:35.266
Time has come for them to realize where are they.

00:01:35.426 --> 00:01:38.466
That’s why they are afraid 
to join European community.

00:01:42.716 --> 00:01:45.036
In no way(-) They are all mediocres in everything.

00:01:45.036 --> 00:01:48.236
Everything they do is mediocre.

