should become a republic in front of the Queen.

00:01:54.956 --> 00:01:56.556
The Queen was sitting there,  

00:01:56.556 --> 00:02:00.396
and the Prime Minister said, in front of 
the Queen, we should become a republic.

00:02:00.396 --> 00:02:04.716
