that the Prime Minister insulted the Queen.

00:02:04.716 --> 00:02:07.255
Shri Mataji: Yes, what did they(-)?

00:02:07.255 --> 00:02:12.876
Yogi: Newspapers in England, they are saying 
that the Australian prime minister insulted  

00:02:12.876 --> 00:02:18.445
the Queen because he said that we should 
become a republic in front of the Queen.

00:02:18.525 --> 00:02:21.485
Shri Mataji: You see now everybody 
is now breaking out of Commonwealth.

00:02:21.485 --> 00:02:23.885
India has also broken, there’s no harm.

00:02:24.925 --> 00:02:31.092
