all that, these things are going on  

00:02:38.482 --> 00:02:42.242
and, I don’t know, they are not so clear-cut.

00:02:42.242 --> 00:02:49.327
Of course, they had an Indian, from, I 
think he was from East Africa who was the  

00:02:50.562 --> 00:03:01.564
President of that, but he’s now gone and that’s 
the reason they must be asking to be republics.

00:03:01.744 --> 00:03:04.784
So it’s no insult to her, I mean 
a declaration is not an insult.

00:03:06.144 --> 00:03:07.628
English are like that.

00:03:08.764 --> 00:03:13.968
They can insult anyone, 
but nobody can insult them.

00:03:14.748 --> 00:03:20.058
Yogi: The Prime Minister’s wife didn’t bow to 
her, didn’t curtsey, and that’s a very big insult.

00:03:20.277 --> 00:03:23.768
Shri Mataji: I didn’t curtsey to her also.

00:03:24.077 --> 00:03:25.608
I never did.

00:03:26.027 --> 00:03:30.747
Actually she bent, thinking I was 
[INAUDIBLE], so I had to lift her up.

00:03:35.690 --> 00:03:38.810
All too much of it, see now, they have these  

00:03:39.370 --> 00:03:42.970
parties, this tea parties, 
means tea party, horrible thing.

00:03:43.530 --> 00:03:49.071
