00:04:01.105 --> 00:04:04.625
and some ladies with the heels, 
they just get pressed into it.

00:04:05.345 --> 00:04:09.955
It’s a mess of a thing, but you have to be there.

00:04:09.971 --> 00:04:13.465
If you are not there they notice you and 
they’ll tell you: ‘Why didn’t you come?’

00:04:13.811 --> 00:04:17.038
But there’s certain qualities in 
English which are to be imbibed.

00:04:17.038 --> 00:04:21.381
Is one of them, they always 
respect work and merit.

00:04:21.571 --> 00:04:26.801
Like they have respected My husband, it’s 
very remarkable I mean, that’s what they do.

00:04:26.851 --> 00:04:30.709
And secondly, they have very good justice.

00:04:30.749 --> 00:04:34.109
[Their] justice system is 
the best in the whole world.

00:04:34.159 --> 00:04:35.929
They cannot be corrupted.

00:04:35.919 --> 00:04:41.439
And thirdly, I would say, as far as the 
Parliament is concerned, and the politicians are  

00:04:41.439 --> 00:04:45.199
concerned, they are very honest, 
[there is] very little of bribery.

00:04:45.199 --> 00:04:47.279
So all this things are there, no doubt.

00:04:47.279 --> 00:04:50.959
But with this austerity of temperament, 
you see, you also develop that kind of a  

00:04:51.519 --> 00:04:55.199
dry nature, arrogance and domination and all that.

00:04:55.199 --> 00:04:58.319
So they are fully on the right 
side, while they should be  

00:04:58.319 --> 00:05:01.940
on the left because they are Shiva’s disciples.

00:05:08.944 --> 00:05:17.184
