everything is fine but the arrogance  

00:05:17.264 --> 00:05:21.224
and living in fools’ paradise is too much.

00:05:23.784 --> 00:05:28.344
I mean, as far as Shakespeare is concerned, 
He was a realized soul of a very high order  

00:05:28.344 --> 00:05:32.404
so He tried to show the futility 
of human endeavor all the time,  

00:05:32.464 --> 00:05:35.674
and also the miracles of God, as in this one.

00:05:36.144 --> 00:05:39.444
But I don’t know if they have understood Him.

00:05:39.494 --> 00:05:43.574
And nowadays there’s not even one play 
running in England, [in] London itself.

00:05:43.574 --> 00:05:47.734
